_sText:
This is my edition of the jurassik park original map.
The original map seems good but too big, I decided to remove you several games, and shrink the map.

Changes:
redistribution of games on the map
delete race games
delete electric Chair game
cage boxes
improved guns games
improved football, the ball left the field and the button was available to prisoners
changed music
automatically kill the losers in the racing cars game
added ladder pipe to return to the cell
friendly fire button added
add secrets
